div.p:
As I see them, our choices are: 

—Do nothing;

—Go back to the 20th parallel which will help a little but not
                                    be a serious reply to the harassment of Saigon;

—After warning the enemy, establish a tit-for-tat policy
                                    towards Hanoi-Haiphong, conducting raids not on a regular basis
                                    but as direct response to attacks on Saigon;

—Go back to Hanoi-Haiphong on a regular basis.
